TMVClassification.py is a PyROOT-based analysis model for TMVA in Python. 

PyROOT requires a Python version > 2.2. More information can be found here:
http://root.cern.ch/root/HowtoPyROOT.html

Notes to the user: 
------------------
Should you encounter window export problems of the following type:

   "Error in <RootX11ErrorHandler>: BadAtom (invalid Atom parameter) (XID: 39, XREQ: 18)"

when importing ROOT classes into python, please add the following lines to 
your /etc/ssh/ssh_config file:

   ForwardX11 yes
   ForwardX11Trusted yes

========================================================================================

